div.div:
Stoplight UIG
For buttons/icons
Represents system and callback states
Rules
- Red: Off, Fail
Yellow: Wait, Unk.
Green: On, Pass
- Callback represented by background button, 4units,
rounded square
- State represented by foreground icon, 2.5-3units,
simple and universally
understandable, supports
fore/backgrounds
- Accessibility:
Dashed or white: Off, Fail
Dotted or gray: Wait, Unk.
Solid thick or black: On, Pass
